==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unjointed
<hw>Un*joint"ed</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Properly p. p. of
<ets>unjoint</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Disjointed; unconnected;
hence, incoherent.</def> <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <ety>[Pref. <ets>un-</ets> + <ets>jointed</ets>.]</ety>
<def>Having no joint or articulation; <as>as, an <ex>unjointed</ex>
stem</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unjust</ent>⟦br⟧
